snippet.title: TERE DIL MEIN - Rito Riba | Elvish Yadav & Jannat Zubair | Rajat Nagpal | Rana Sotal | Anshul Garg
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents Tere Dil Mein featuring Elvish Yadav & Jannat Zubair.

Audio Credits :-
Singer : Rito Riba
Music Composer : Rajat nagpal
Lyrics : Rana sotal
Music composed , produced and programmed by : Rajat Nagpal 
Mixed and Mastered by : Shadab Rayeen 
Guitars : Rhythm Shaw 
Dholak & Tabla Raju : Sardar and Team 
Chorus : Sonu

Lyrics :-
Rabb maan liya tujhko 
Jagg maan liya tujhko 
Tu he hai dunia meri 
Sabb maan liya tujhko,,

Maanga  jo paaya vahi  ,,

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

Bachkay ray bachkay deewane,,
Tu naino kay khel na jaane ,,


Tu meri jaan hai yaara ,,
Tu he hai jaan say pyara ,,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara
Dhadkan banke rehna yaara ,,
Apna mujhey kehna yaara ,
Sunali ve Sunlai ve dildara ,

Tujhey yaar kahay
Jisay pyaar kahay 
Humey toh hogea hai vahi , 

Dekh tere dil may 
Dil may dil may 
Dil may dil may yaara  toh nhi
Mai khogea khogea ,,
khogea khogea khogea yaara hu kahi ,,

#teredilmein #elvishyadav #elvish #jannat #jannatzubair #ritoriba

Experience the divine power of the Subramanya Sahasranama Stotram, containing the 1000 Names of Lord Murugan. Chanting or listening to this sacred hymn from the Skanda Purana is the ultimate remedy for all planetary afflictions.

Lord Karthikeya, also known as Shanmukha and Skanda, is the commander of the divine army. Listening to his Sahasranamam on Tuesdays (Mangalavaram) and during Shasti is widely believed to remove Kuja Dosha (Mars Affliction) and Sarpa Dosha (Snake Curse), paving the way for a happy marriage ("Kalyana Prapti") and blessed children ("Santana Prapti").

Whether you are facing legal battles, enemies, or health issues, the vibration of these 1000 names acts as a protective shield like the holy Vel. Let this Telugu Devotional Video bring the blessings of Palani Andava to your home.

snippet.title: Hawaon Ne Yeh Kaha (Lyrical Video) | Udit Narayan | Hrithik Roshan | Ameesha Patel
snippet.description:
Hawaon Ne Yeh Kaha is a soft and romantic melody sung by Udit Narayan, featuring the beautiful pairing of Hrithik Roshan and Ameesha Patel from the movie Aap Mujhe Achche Lagne Lage. 
This song captures young love, innocence, and heartfelt emotions beautifully, making it a timeless favourite for Bollywood romance lovers. 

Credits: 
Singer: Udit Narayan
Music: Rajesh Roshan
Lyrics: Dev Kohli
Movie: Aap Mujhe Achche Lagne Lage
Starring: Hrithik Roshan, Ameesha Patel
Director: Vikram Bhatt
Producer: Rohit Kumar
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 

[Nahin marna ganwara pyaar mein 

Tumse yeh kehna hai 

Tumhein bhi zinda rehna hai 

Mujhe bhi zinda rehna hai] 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil 

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil 

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Magar jo pyaar karte hain 

Kabhi bharte nahin aahein 


Hawaon ne yeh kaha 

Fizaon ne yeh kaha 

Aayi pyaar ki ye rut badi tufani 

Tu darna na o meri rani 

Badlega yeh mausam ari deewani 

Hum likhenge prem kahani 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil 

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Kabhi aasaan, kabhi mushkil 

Ajab hain pyaar ki raahein 

Magar jo pyaar karte hain 

Kabhi bharte nahin aahein 

Hawaon ne yeh kaha 

Fizaon ne yeh kaha 

Aayi pyaar ki ye rut badi tufani 

Tu darna na o meri rani 

Badlega yeh mausam ari deewani 

Hum likhenge prem kahani
